s</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/taft-bulletin">Taft Bulletin</a></li><li><a href="/about/taft-voices">Taft Voices</a></li><li><a href="https://www.taftphotos.com/" target="_blank">Taft Photos<span class="fsStyleSROnly" data-nosnippet="">(opens in new window/tab)</span></a></li><li><a href="/transcripts">Transcripts</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="students"><a href="/students">Students</a></li><li class="fsNavParentPage parents"><a href="/parents">Parents</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/parents/portal">Portal</a></li><li><a href="/parents/grandparent-information-form">Grandparent Information Form</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage alumni"><a href="/alumni">Alumni</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/alumni/reunions">Alumni Weekend: May 8-9, 2026</a></li><li><a href="/bulletin">Taft Bulletin</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/horace-dutton-taft-alumni-medal">Horace Dutton Taft Alumni Medal</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/update-name-address-email">Update Name/Address/Email</a></li><li><a href="/transcripts/registrar-transcript-request">Request a Transcript</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/calendar">Events</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/e-newsletter-archive">E-Newsletter Archive</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/alumni-volunteer-opportunities">Alumni Volunteer Opportunities</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/rhino-crash-20">Rhino Crash 2.0</a></li><li><a href="/alumni/taft-alumni-career-connections">Taft Alumni Career Connections</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="search"><a href="/search-results">Search Results</a></li></ul></nav>
