	<div class="fsElement fsNavigation fsList nav-main" id="fsEl_1774" data-use-new="true" >

				<div class="fsElementContent" >
		<nav><ul class="fsNavLevel1"><li class="fsNavParentPage"><a href="/about">About</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription"><div>More than a century has passed since Mr. Taft founded our school. While the world and the school have changed dramatically, his fundamental values endure: work hard, without regard for public acclaim; develop all your talents: academic, artistic, and athletic; and most importantly, give of yourself to others.</div>
</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/about/head-of-school-peter-becker-95">Head of School Peter Becker '95 </a></li><li><a href="/about/mission-and-motto">Mission and Motto</a></li><li><a href="/about/commitment-to-diversity-equity-and-inclusion">Commitment to Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion (DEI)</a></li><li><a href="/about/our-history">Our History</a></li><li><a href="/about/taft-voices">Taft Voices</a></li><li><a href="/about/portrait-of-a-learner">Portrait of a Learner</a></li><li><a href="/about/honor-code">Honor Code</a></li><li><a href="/about/mascot-and-colors">Mascot and Colors</a></li><li><a href="/multimedia">Multimedia</a></li><li><a href="/about/spiritual-life">Spiritual Life</a></li><li><a href="/about/taft-by-the-numbers">Taft by the Numbers</a></li><li><a href="/about/trustees">Trustees</a></li><li><a href="/about/campus-map">Campus Map</a></li><li><a href="/about/careers-at-taft">Careers at Taft</a></li><li><a href="/about/welcome-to-watertown">Welcome to Watertown</a></li><li><a href="/about/social-media">Social Media</a></li><li><a href="/about/strategic-design">Strategic Design</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage"><a href="/admission">Admission</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription"><div>“The Taft Admission office seeks students who will infuse our community with intellectual and social curiosity, while embracing a joyful balance and a steadfast commitment to excellence in all they pursue.’’<em><strong>Amanda Bohnsack, Director of Enrollment</strong></em></div>
</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="https://slate.taftschool.org/portal/taft" target="_blank">Inquire/Request Viewbook<span class="fsStyleSROnly" data-nosnippet="">(opens in new window/tab)</span></a></li><li><a href="/admission/plan-your-visit">Plan Your Visit</a></li><li><a href="https://vimeo.com/459158772/8007902927" target="_blank">Virtual Tour<span class="fsStyleSROnly" data-nosnippet="">(opens in new window/tab)</span></a></li><li><a href="/admission/webinars">Events and Webinars</a></li><li><a href="/admission/inside-taft-a-virtual-visit">Inside Taft: A Virtual Visit</a></li><li><a href="/admission/apply-to-taft">Apply to Taft</a></li><li><a href="/admission/affording-taft">Affording Taft</a></li><li><a href="/admission/international-students">International Students</a></li><li><a href="/admission/meet-our-team">Meet Our Team</a></li><li><a href="/admission/taft-voices">Taft Voices</a></li><li><a href="/admission/portal-access">Portal Access</a></li><li><a href="/admission/10-reasons-to-apply-to-taft">Why Taft?</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage"><a href="/academics">Academics</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription">Our students develop the skills, knowledge, and habits of mind to be lifelong learners, critical thinkers, and responsible global citizens.</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/academics/academic-departments">Academic Departments</a></li><li><a href="/academics/course-listings">Course Listings</a></li><li><a href="/academics/college-counseling">College Counseling</a></li><li><a href="/academics/moorhead-academic-center">Moorhead Academic Center</a></li><li><a href="/academics/academic-assessments-and-resources/resources-for-learning">Academic Assessments and Resources</a></li><li><a href="/academics/innovations-in-learning">Innovations in Learning</a></li><li><a href="/academics/library">Hulbert Taft Jr. Library</a></li><li><a href="/academics/faculty-directory">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href="/academics/summer-reading">Summer Reading</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage arts"><a href="/arts">Arts</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription"><div>Success in the Arts is bred of self-confidence; a fearlessness or joy in the process, more than the outcome.</div>
</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li class="programs"><a href="/arts/programs">Programs</a></li><li><a href="/arts/programs/fine-arts">Fine Arts</a></li><li><a href="/arts/programs/performing-arts">Performing Arts</a></li><li><a href="/arts/programs/music">Music</a></li><li><a href="/arts/programs/film">Film</a></li><li class="gallery"><a href="/arts/mark-w-potter-gallery">Mark W. Potter Gallery</a></li><li class="concert"><a href="/arts/concert-series">Concert Series</a></li><li class="quicklinks"><a href="/arts/quicklinks">Quicklinks</a></li><li class="search"><a href="/search-results">Search</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage"><a href="/athletics">Athletics</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription">In building one of the most successful athletic programs in New England, Taft coaches promote fair play, respect for opponents, a love of the game, competitive spirit, and team loyalty.</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/athletics/schedule">Schedule</a></li><li><a href="/athletics/scores">Scores</a></li><li><a href="/athletics/teams">Teams</a></li><li><a href="/athletics/athletics-news">News</a></li><li><a href="/athletics/coaches">Coaches</a></li><li><a href="/athletics/facilities">Facilities</a></li><li><a href="/athletics/multimedia">Multimedia</a></li><li><a href="/admission/inquire">Inquire</a></li><li><a href="/athletics/livestream">Livestream</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage"><a href="/campus-life">Campus Life</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription">Taft is a school with heart. Our sense of community is strong, and extends to every aspect of campus life.</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/campus-life/daily-life">Daily Life</a></li><li><a href="/campus-life/living-on-campus">Living on Campus</a></li><li><a href="/campus-life/clubs-activities-and-student-leadership">Clubs, Activities, and Student Leadership</a></li><li><a href="/campus-life/health-wellness">Health &amp; Wellness</a></li><li><a href="/multimedia">Multimedia</a></li><li><a href="/about/campus-map">Campus Map</a></li><li><a href="/students">Student Portal</a></li><li><a href="http://taftschool.3dcartstores.com/" target="_blank">Store<span class="fsStyleSROnly" data-nosnippet="">(opens in new window/tab)</span></a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage"><a href="/giving">Giving</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription">Taft has been built, brick by brick, through the collective generosity of generations of alumni, parents, families, and friends.</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/giving/founders-society">Founders Society</a></li><li><a href="/giving/taft-fund">Taft Fund</a></li><li><a href="http://plannedgiving.taftschool.org/" target="_blank">Planned Giving<span class="fsStyleSROnly" data-nosnippet="">(opens in new window/tab)</span></a></li><li><a href="/giving/endowed-funds">Endowed Funds</a></li><li><a href="/alumni">Alumni</a></li><li><a href="/giving/ways-to-give">Ways to Give</a></li><li><a href="https://www.givecampus.com/campaigns/65822/donations/new?a=10814234" target="_blank">Make a Gift<span class="fsStyleSROnly" data-nosnippet="">(opens in new window/tab)</span></a></li><li><a href="/giving/contact">Contact the Alumni and Development Office</a></li><li><a href="https://taftconnect.org/" target="_blank">Taft Connect<span class="fsStyleSROnly" data-nosnippet="">(opens in new window/tab)</span></a></li><li><a href="/giving/matching-gifts">Matching Gifts</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="fsNavParentPage"><a href="/living-our-motto">Living Our Motto</a><div class="fsNavPageInfo"><div class="fsNavPageDescription">Not to be served but to serve is more than our motto, it is the underlying principle that shapes our perspectives and guides our actions every day.</div><ul class="fsNavLevel2"><li><a href="/living-our-motto/community-service">Community Service Programs and Organizations</a></li><li><a href="/living-our-motto/global-leadership-institute">Global Leadership Institute</a></li><li><a href="/living-our-motto/global-studies-and-service-diploma">Global Studies and Service Diploma</a></li><li><a href="/living-our-motto/environmental-initiatives-and-sustainability">Environmental Initiatives and Sustainability</a></li><li><a href="/living-our-motto/morning-meetings">Bringing the World to Taft: Morning Meeting Speaker Series</a></li></ul></div></li><li><a href="/athletics/livestream">Livestream</a></li></ul></nav>
	</div>


	</div>
	
